comments: Jordan (BKN) establishes is screening position in path of Anderson (MEM) and absorbs the contact.
Luwawu-Cabarrot (BKN) makes marginal contact to Brooks' (MEM) leg on his driving shot attempt.
Valanciunas (MEM) and LeVert (BKN) engage and disengage during rebounding.
Anderson (MEM) momentarily places his hand to LeVert's (BKN) front at the start of his drive and quickly removes running alongside of him to the basket.
Chiozza (BKN) extends his leg in Valanciunas' (MEM) path during his shooting motion and contact affects the play at the basket.
Anderson (MEM) makes marginal contact to LeVert's (BKN) front as he momentarily loses the ball as he goes over the screen.
Valanciunas (MEM) establishes legal position in Harris' (BKN) path during the pick and gives him room to avoid contact.
Luwawu-Cabarrot (BKN) makes hand on ball contact and deflects the pass away from Valanciunas (MEM). Any ensuing contact is deemed incidental.
Jordan (BKN) makes marginal contact to Valanciunas' (MEM) back while the ball is loose.
Valanciunas (MEM) makes marginal contact to Green and releases as he receives the inbound ball.
Anderson (MEM) makes incidental "high-five" contact with LeVert (BKN) after the release of his jump shot attempt.
LeVert (BKN) makes contact to Brooks' (MEM) arm during the pick and contact affects his ability to maintain control of the ball.
Jordan (BKN) makes incidental contact to Jones' (MEM) arm after the release of his driving shot attempt.
Jordan (BKN) establishes legal position in Anderson's (MEM) path during the pick and gives him a step to avoid contact.
LeVert (BKN) establishes a legal guarding position in Anderson's (MEM) path and absorbs the contact during his drive to the basket.
Valanciunas (MEM) maintains legal guarding position and cleanly blocks LeVert's (BKN) driving shot attempt. Any ensuing contact is deemed incidental.
Anderson (MEM) beats Luwawau-Cabarrot (BKN) to the spot and absorbs the contact during his drive to the basket.
Clarke (MEM) makes marginal contact with Luwawu-Cabarrot (BKN) when contact occurs at the end of his drive.
Harris (BKN) legally contest Brooks' (MEM) driving shot attempt.
Jordan (BKN) establishes legal position in Jones' (MEM) path firming up and makes some contact as they disengage..
Jones (MEM) makes incidental contact to Chiozza's (BKN) arm after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Jordan (BKN) touched the ball while it is in the imaginary cylinder above the rim.

Replay review of the foul called on Green (BKN) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  Green (BKN) makes contact to Clarke's (MEM) side that dislodges him from his rebounding position.
LeVert (BKN) commits a take foul on Allen (MEM).
Clarke (MEM) and LeVert (BKN) engage and disengage off ball prior to the inbound pass.
Brooks (MEM) places a resting hand to Harris' (BKN) side during his drive and removes it prior to the start of his upward shooting motion.
LeVert (BKN) commits a take foul on Anderson (MEM).
Green (BKN) and Valanciunas (MEM) engage and disengage during rebounding.
Harris (BKN) makes contact to Anderson's (MEM) lower body and affects his shot attempt.
